      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "You Had Me at Poofy",
        "Client": "Excited Entrepreneur",
        "Description": "OK, picture this: Royal Ludroth\r\nstuffed animals. Eh? EH? You can\r\ntotally see it, right? With their little\r\npoofy mane, they\u0027d be a hit! And\r\nwhy stop there? Kitchen sponges,\r\nbath sponges!? All we need is\r\na little...\u0022product research.\u0022",
